        <section class="block intro">
            <div class="container">
                
                    <header>
                        
                            
                                <h1>Hundreds gathered in NYC for a guerrilla debut of The NSA Video -- narrated by Evangeline Lilly and projected onto the side of a building in Manhattan!</h1>
                            
                        
                    </header>
                
                
                    
                        





<section class="block group">
    <div class="container">
        
        <div class="text">
            

            

            

            <p>Tuesday night, hundreds gathered in Washington Square Park to witness the debut of our brand new NSA video, which is narrated by actress Evangeline Lilly (best known for her role as Kate Austen in Lost.)</p>
<p>While supporters spilled out into the street, we projected the film onto the side of a large Manhattan building.</p>
<p>See our <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1TD4PCFNrDmlJXT2MOn8yT1jBbmP_aoKNUMDhXPcJvV8/pub">press release here.</a></p>
<p>There's a <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vq1kQEPJLlw&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;amp;a">great video of the launch here.</a></p>
<p>Check out the images in the gallery below!</p>
<iframe class="imgur-album" width="100%" height="550" frameborder="0" src="http://imgur.com/a/MCpMv/embed"></iframe>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

                    
                        





<section class="block group has-image">
    <div class="container">
        
            <figure class="bordered">
                <img src="https://old-cms-assets.fightforthefuture.org/media/campaigns/blocks/thumbnails/nsa_eye.jpg.400x0_q85.jpg" />
            </figure>
        
        <div class="text">
            
                <h1>The NSA doesn&#39;t want this video out there. </h1>
            

            

            

            <p>Please share the info below far and wide! Come meet us in Washington Square Park!
<br></br>
<b>What?</b>
A celebratory gathering to launch our definitive video about NSA
surveillance -- featuring a celebrity voice-over from actress <a href="http://www.evangeline-lilly.net/">Evangeline
Lilly</a> -- projected larger-than-life on the side of a building in
bustling Manhattan!
<br></br>
<b>When?</b> Tuesday, October 15th. 9:00pm (sharp!) - 9:45pm.
<br></br>
<b>Where?</b> Washington Square Park, NYC. Gather at the Arch.
<br></br>
Join internet &amp; freedom lovers from across New York for a quick and fun
event celebrating the launch of our new humorous and educational video
about NSA surveillance -- projected on the side of a building during a
guerrilla screening near Washington Square Park. We’re unveiling the
video in a <em>very</em> public way to maximize it’s movement-building
potential, and we need you there to help draw a crowd of spectators and
the media. Plus, you’ll be one of the first people in the world to see
this groundbreaking short film!
<br></br>
We’ll be giving out popcorn and signing people up to attend the <a href="http://rally.stopwatching.us">Stop Watching Us Rally Against Mass Surveillance</a> in Washington DC on the anniversary of the PATRIOT Act, October 26th. Come be part of the spectacle and meet other like-minded New Yorkers while we officially launch a game-changing video about government surveillance. If you want to help out with handing out popcorn or flyers, let us know:
<a href="&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#116;&#101;&#97;&#109;&#64;&#102;&#105;&#103;&#104;&#116;&#102;&#111;&#114;&#116;&#104;&#101;&#102;&#117;&#116;&#117;&#114;&#101;&#46;&#111;&#114;&#103;">&#116;&#101;&#97;&#109;&#64;&#102;&#105;&#103;&#104;&#116;&#102;&#111;&#114;&#116;&#104;&#101;&#102;&#117;&#116;&#117;&#114;&#101;&#46;&#111;&#114;&#103;</a>
<br></br>
<b>Hosted by:</b> <a href="http://fightforthefuture.org">Fight for the Future</a>, <a href="http://demandprogress.org">Demand Progress</a>, <a href="http://restorethefourthnyc.org/">NYC Restore the 4th</a>, <a href="http://bordc.org">Bill of Rights Defense Committee</a>, and <a href="http://theilluminator.org/">The Illuminator</a>.</p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

                    
                
            </div>
        </section>

        
            

